{"tha-ap426:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap426:0.2":"Sakimsammajjakavagga ","tha-ap426:0.3":"Sattakadambapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap426:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap426:1.2":"kukkuto nama pabbato; ","tha-ap426:1.3":"Tamhi pabbatapadamhi, ","tha-ap426:1.4":"satta buddha vasimsu te. ","tha-ap426:2.1":"Kadambam pupphitam disva, ","tha-ap426:2.2":"paggahetvana anjalim; ","tha-ap426:2.3":"Satta mala gahetvana, ","tha-ap426:2.4":"punnacittena okirim. ","tha-ap426:3.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap426:3.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap426:3.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap426:3.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap426:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap426:4.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap426:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap426:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap426:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap426:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap426:5.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap426:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap426:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap426:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap426:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap426:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap426:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap426:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sattakadambapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap426:9.1":"Sattakadambapupphiyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}